high_descs: Move to the table left side of the table ahead of you
pick up a spatula from the table
Move to the center of the table
put the spatula in a pan on the table
pick up the pan from the table
move to the sink to the right of you
put the pan in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a spatula in the sink.

high_descs: Go to the left, then hang a right to go to the other side of the table where the spatula is.
Pick up the spatula that is on the table between the tomato and the skillet.
Raise the spatula up in the air.
Put the spatula in to the skillet next to the toaster.
Pick up the skillet with the spatula in it that is on the table.
Turn to the right and go to the sink.
Put the skillet with the spatula in it in to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a skillet with a spatula in it in a sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk around the table.
Pick up the spatula in the middle of the table.
Look up at the pan on the table.
Put the spatula in the pan.
Pick up the pan with the spatula in it.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the pan and spatula in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the spatula and pan in the sink.
